twitter.name: Twitter
twitter.description: Makes the target cronge due to twitter, has a chance to poison aswell

charge_boost.name: Charge Boost
charge_boost.description: Increases the user's stats depending on charge

counter.name: Counter
counter.description: Deals double the damage taken. This move ignores the target's defense and is always done last

troll.name: Troll
troll.description: Does a little trolling and makes the target's hp % be the same as the user's, will fail if the user's hp is greater than 25%

bloc.name: Bloc
bloc.description: Blocks incoming damage, success rate is lower if it's used repeatedly
